Package: PBWG
Title: Data Preparation for International ANS Performance Benchmarking
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Rainer",
      family = "Koelle",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "rainer.koelle+pbwg@example.com"
    )
Description: Provides a tidyverse-oriented workflow for reading,
    decoding, harmonising, and preparing extracted data used in
    international operational ANS performance benchmarking projects.
    The package is designed to start from warehouse extracts and later
    accommodate alternative interfaces such as SQL queries or data
    platform connectors.
